************************************************************************
* Purpose        : Load object data identified by I_BUSINESS_KEY_TAB
*                  from DB to DB_DATA Table
*
* Version        : 2.0
*
* Precondition   : I_BUSINESS_KEY_TAB is a table of valid business keys
*
